title: Good Riddance - (2015) Peace in Our Time (WebRip) - Nrv
description:
Good Riddance's upcoming 2015 new album, PEACE IN OUR TIME.
Since there is NO release yet of this album in the torrents world, I decided to share what I could fetch on the web while the album is officially released on the market.
This is a rip from the web (stream), so I have no control over the quality obtained, which IS a good quality by the way, but it is NOT a 320kbps release. The web quality probably was something like 192kbps. It got ripped to WAV and then compressed to VBR MP3.
So the quality is very decent, especially for a temporary release.
Please buy this album when it's available, if you like it!!

Enjoy this fast melodic punk rock album to the max!
